Who knows the answer?

28:16.697 --> 28:18.281
Me! Me! Me!

28:18.282 --> 28:19.657
Two! It's two!

28:19.658 --> 28:21.285
That's right! You're a genius!

28:22.578 --> 28:26.330
- What does this English word mean?
