28:26.331 --> 28:28.875
The answer is: "Big ass."

28:28.876 --> 28:30.335
You sex-crazed girl!

28:31.461 --> 28:34.547
Huh... So this is what school is like.

28:34.548 --> 28:36.216
I think I've got the hang of it now.

28:37.843 --> 28:41.220
