you didn't even go to elementary school?

28:41.221 --> 28:42.764
Huh? Yeah.

28:43.390 --> 28:47.852
Isn't that... bad?

28:47.853 --> 28:49.354
Bad?

28:50.230 --> 28:51.648
Well, not bad.

28:52.316 --> 28:53.483
It's weird.

28:55.569 --> 28:58.363
A 16-year-old is still a kid.

28:58.864 --> 29:01.115
Normally, you'd study for entrance exams,

29:01.116 --> 29:04.745
