41:04.298 --> 41:09.052
<i>♪ In a park ♪</i>

41:10.053 --> 41:13.849
<i>♪ We will go to an aquarium ♪</i>

41:15.559 --> 41:19.354
<i>♪ And we will see dolphins and penguins ♪</i>

41:20.898 --> 41:25.736
<i>♪ Loved by Jane ♪</i>

41:26.236 --> 41:29.655
<i>♪ We will rest after lunch ♪</i>

41:29.656 --> 41:35.078
<i>♪ So, what did we do in the morning? ♪</i>

41:35.787 --> 41:39.750
<i>♪ We will speak about it ♪</i>

41:41.168 --> 41:45.005
<i>♪ Until we remember ♪</i>

41:46.465 --> 41:50.469
<i>♪ We won't remember ♪</i>

41:51.512 --> 41:56.558
<i>♪ And we will sleep
At the church that night ♪</i>

42:25.879 --> 42:28.590
You're the one who made the storm
to trap us inside the building.

42:29.174 --> 42:30.175
Right, Typhoon?

42:31.051 --> 42:33.720
I didn't know you were here, Lady Reze.

42:34.471 --> 42:36.806
I'll turn a blind eye
to what you did today.

42:36.807 --> 42:39.392
In exchange, you'll obey me for a while.

42:39.393 --> 42:42.229
Go deal with his body.

42:59.913 --> 43:02.373
Hmm.

43:02.374 --> 43:03.792
Huh?

43:15.762 --> 43:17.431
- Boo!
- Whoa!

44:49.106 --> 44:53.025
I heard about this place
from the owner of the café I work at.

44:53.026 --> 44:55.194
He said it's the best spot
to watch fireworks.

44:55.195 --> 44:58.031
No one else ever comes here.
It's a secret spot.

44:58.991 --> 45:01.034
Huh...

45:15.048 --> 45:16.300
Hey, Denji.

45:17.009 --> 45:19.052
I've been thinking a lot these days.

45:20.053 --> 45:23.306
I think your current situation is weird.

45:23.307 --> 45:26.309
You're only 16,
but they're not letting you go to school.

45:26.310 --> 45:28.312
And they're making you kill devils.

45:28.896 --> 45:30.939
It's not something
this country should allow.

45:37.529 --> 45:40.449
Why don't you quit your job
and run away with me.

45:40.991 --> 45:43.911
I'll make you happy.

45:44.745 --> 45:46.538
I'll protect you
for the rest of your life.

45:47.915 --> 45:49.082
Please.

45:54.630 --> 45:57.341
Run away? Where?

45:58.175 --> 45:59.967
I'll ask my friend.

45:59.968 --> 46:03.429
My friend has a place
where Public Safety will never find you.

46:03.430 --> 46:05.431
It won't happen right away,

46:05.432 --> 46:07.518
but we can go to school
together there someday.

46:08.727 --> 46:10.521
Why would you do all that for me?

46:11.939 --> 46:13.607
Because...

46:14.399 --> 46:16.276
I like you, Denji.

46:26.286 --> 46:28.580
Why are you having
such a hard time deciding?

46:29.540 --> 46:31.208
Denji, do you hate me?

46:31.792 --> 46:33.085
I like you!

46:34.461 --> 46:35.462
But...

46:36.046 --> 46:39.049
I've just recently started
to feel appreciated at work.

46:39.716 --> 46:42.469
I can go farther away without supervision.

46:43.470 --> 46:47.349
I'm gradually learning how to deal with
my buddy, who has a shitty personality.

46:48.809 --> 46:52.563
And I've finally started to become friends
with my difficult senior colleague.

46:53.689 --> 46:56.149
And I've found a goal
to work towards at work.

46:56.942 --> 46:59.361
Things are starting to get fun now.

47:00.696 --> 47:04.741
Can't I keep seeing you
while I continue to work?

47:07.953 --> 47:10.497
- The fireworks are about to begin!
- This way, please!

47:13.375 --> 47:14.501
I see.

47:15.169 --> 47:16.211
I understand.

47:18.755 --> 47:19.756
Denji.

47:20.591 --> 47:24.302
There's someone else you like, right?

48:47.261 --> 48:48.428
It hurts, doesn't it?

48:48.929 --> 48:50.430
I'm sorry.

48:58.397 --> 49:01.817
Denji, I'm going to take your heart. Okay?

49:08.282 --> 49:10.324
Dash!

49:10.325 --> 49:11.827
Huh?

49:19.293 --> 49:21.961
Run away! Run away!
We're in trouble! We're in trouble!

49:21.962 --> 49:25.089
How come I didn't notice anything
from the smell?

49:25.090 --> 49:27.592
She's dangerous, Lord Chainsaw!

49:27.593 --> 49:30.512
That smell...

49:31.180 --> 49:34.892
She's the Bomb Devil!

49:38.937 --> 49:40.314
Boom.

50:06.173 --> 50:07.174
You thief.

50:35.202 --> 50:36.495
Lord Chainsaw!

50:50.634 --> 50:53.302
Are you from Division 4 too?

50:53.303 --> 50:56.223
I'll let you go if you leave Denji there
and leave right now.

51:03.981 --> 51:05.774
Oh. I see.

51:20.247 --> 51:21.748
Hmm?

51:35.512 --> 51:38.974
Damn. I wanted to go to the festival.

51:39.474 --> 51:41.642
Whoa. She's killing something.

51:41.643 --> 51:44.188
We've encountered a devil
near the festival.

51:45.147 --> 51:47.191
2034.

51:47.858 --> 51:49.610
The battle begins.

51:50.277 --> 51:52.695
Are you private Devil Hunters?

51:52.696 --> 51:54.780
Whoa. She said something.

51:54.781 --> 51:56.867
This one's really strong.

52:17.888 --> 52:19.389
They sure ran away fast!

52:20.557 --> 52:22.476
DEVIL EXTERMINATION DIVISION 2
FUCHŪ TRAINING FACILITY

52:34.446 --> 52:35.656
Match over!

52:36.281 --> 52:37.991
Thank you.

52:40.285 --> 52:42.996
Thank you for your instruction.

52:44.373 --> 52:45.707
Aki.

52:46.583 --> 52:49.335
Thanks for coming.

52:49.336 --> 52:51.420
I can't say no to you, Nomo.

52:51.421 --> 52:55.716
Whoa! Really?
Then come back to Division 2!

52:55.717 --> 52:59.345
All the stories I hear about
the Special Division sound so gory anyway.

52:59.346 --> 53:03.516
If everything goes well, I'm going
to become the sub-captain in five years.

53:03.517 --> 53:06.103
When that happens,
I'm going to invite you to join.

53:07.896 --> 53:09.356
Thank you very much.

53:12.568 --> 53:13.610
<i>Hey.</i>

53:14.236 --> 53:16.697
You haven't told him
that you'll be dead in five years?

53:17.865 --> 53:20.366
Who did you hear that from?

53:20.367 --> 53:21.869
From Power.

53:22.494 --> 53:23.954
That damn devil.

53:25.455 --> 53:26.999
Don't tell anyone.

53:28.709 --> 53:30.501
You're so lucky.

53:30.502 --> 53:32.671
I want to die soon too.

53:33.839 --> 53:36.549
As long as I'm alive, I have to work hard.

53:36.550 --> 53:38.719
If I die,
I won't have to work hard anymore.

53:40.220 --> 53:41.722
Oh, that reminds me...

53:42.306 --> 53:44.683
You have a contract
with the Future Devil, right?

53:45.184 --> 53:46.893
Why don't you try asking it?

53:46.894 --> 53:48.687
Ask it when I'm going to die.

53:49.938 --> 53:51.148
I refuse.

53:52.733 --> 53:55.526
Aki! Come downstairs! Now!

53:57.279 --> 54:00.240
He showed up at the entrance and
claimed he's from the Special Division.

54:01.241 --> 54:03.910
Is this fiend really on our side?

54:03.911 --> 54:05.412
Y-Yes.

54:05.913 --> 54:09.166
Did a devil do this to Denji?

54:10.250 --> 54:13.045
Bomb is coming... Bomb...

54:13.712 --> 54:16.297
She's one of the Gun Devil's allies!

54:18.300 --> 54:20.676
How do you know that?

54:23.013 --> 54:24.181
Answer me.

54:24.806 --> 54:27.434
I could kill you right here
if I wanted to.

54:28.519 --> 54:30.561
If I tell you, they'll kill me.

54:30.562 --> 54:32.438
I promised Makima.

54:32.439 --> 54:33.940
Makima?

54:33.941 --> 54:35.566
Ah!

54:35.567 --> 54:37.694
There she is! Bomb's here!

54:45.494 --> 54:46.870
Hey, beautiful lady!

54:47.496 --> 54:49.498
Don't come any closer!

54:49.998 --> 54:52.708
This place is a training facility
for Devil Extermination Division 2.

54:52.709 --> 54:55.546
Members of the public
are not allowed to enter.

54:57.339 --> 54:59.173
Excuse me!

55:01.260 --> 55:02.301
Reze...

55:02.302 --> 55:03.678
Reze?

55:03.679 --> 55:06.222
Please help me!

55:06.223 --> 55:08.934
I'm being attacked by a devil!

55:09.560 --> 55:10.560
Oh.

55:10.561 --> 55:13.271
She's sure smiling a lot
for someone under attack.

55:13.272 --> 55:15.231
- Nomo.
- Yeah.

55:15.232 --> 55:17.441
Take your friend with you
and stay in the back.

55:17.442 --> 55:18.693
Okay.

55:18.694 --> 55:22.613
Contact headquarters and the vice-captain.
Summon all Division 2 members.

55:22.614 --> 55:24.156
Okay!

55:24.157 --> 55:25.325
And...

55:25.993 --> 55:28.704
Have you seen that beauty
somewhere before?

55:29.288 --> 55:31.706
Now's not the right time
to try to pick up women.

55:31.707 --> 55:34.209
No, I'm being serious.

55:37.504 --> 55:40.590
It can't be true. There's no way.

55:40.591 --> 55:43.342
Thanks. I'm counting on you.

55:43.343 --> 55:44.720
You owe me one.

55:46.638 --> 55:48.223
Kato! Tanabe!

55:49.099 --> 55:51.684
I'll treat you to dinner
if you can kill that woman.

55:51.685 --> 55:54.730
Don't assume she's a human.
Handle her like you would a devil.

55:55.355 --> 55:58.065
I guess it didn't work.

55:58.066 --> 55:59.610
It's not working.

56:00.903 --> 56:02.613
In that case, I've got no choice.

56:04.740 --> 56:06.992
I'll just have to kill everyone.

56:13.332 --> 56:14.498
Blood?

56:14.499 --> 56:17.169
We've caused mold to grow
in her heart and intestines.

56:17.669 --> 56:20.254
She's throwing up blood. It's working.

56:20.255 --> 56:23.258
Even if she drinks blood and regenerates,
the mold's not going to disappear.

56:24.176 --> 56:26.261
Now we just need to buy some time.

56:29.348 --> 56:30.516
Hmm?

56:33.519 --> 56:35.062
She inflicted damage to herself!

56:37.898 --> 56:39.607
Are you able to grow mold on her brain?

56:39.608 --> 56:41.818
We can only do it if the target's alive.

56:51.411 --> 56:52.537
Boo.

57:00.420 --> 57:02.839
She's a devil! A devil is here!

57:02.840 --> 57:05.675
She went right!
Don't let her get near Aki!

57:05.676 --> 57:07.386
Nomo! Behind you!

57:09.888 --> 57:11.139
Kon!

57:15.602 --> 57:17.062
Ah--

57:28.740 --> 57:31.493
There she is! There's the devil!

57:34.955 --> 57:37.498
Masaki Ando,
requesting permission to fire!

57:37.499 --> 57:38.876
Permission granted!

57:50.345 --> 57:52.598
In Japan,
do you need permission to fire a gun?

57:53.932 --> 57:54.933
Kon!

58:00.939 --> 58:02.941
You're pretty stubborn.

58:04.026 --> 58:06.862
Now that's a real sight for sore eyes.

58:12.451 --> 58:13.660
Kon.

58:20.584 --> 58:22.502
Excuse me for a moment.

58:22.503 --> 58:24.253
Vice-captain!

58:24.254 --> 58:27.341
That was close.

58:28.550 --> 58:31.135
What's that taste?

58:31.136 --> 58:34.472
- Huh?
- I hate this taste.

58:34.473 --> 58:35.682
I'm going home now.

58:40.270 --> 58:42.814
I was supposed to go
to a singles mixer today.

58:43.315 --> 58:46.068
Take me with you next time.

58:47.986 --> 58:51.364
I'll drive. You have them
drink some of your blood.

58:51.365 --> 58:52.949
Huh?

58:52.950 --> 58:54.618
I guess I've got no choice.

58:58.205 --> 59:00.624
Aren't you going to start the car?

59:01.458 --> 59:02.876
Damn.

59:03.460 --> 59:06.379
It showed me a future
I didn't want to see.

59:06.380 --> 59:07.463
Huh?

59:18.725 --> 59:20.393
That monster.

59:20.394 --> 59:24.146
I killed them to show you
how powerful I am.

59:24.147 --> 59:26.525
I don't want to kill anyone if possible.

59:27.860 --> 59:30.862
Take Denji out of the car and leave.

59:45.961 --> 59:49.673
The gasoline is going to
make that car burn to a crisp.

59:53.844 --> 59:56.221
What a pain.

59:57.764 --> 59:59.266
Acho!

01:00:03.854 --> 01:00:05.855
I asked the Special Division for backup.

01:00:05.856 --> 01:00:07.149
They saved us.

01:00:13.739 --> 01:00:15.115
No way!

01:00:16.658 --> 01:00:19.620
I kicked with everything I got just now.

01:00:20.579 --> 01:00:22.164
Nice kick.

01:00:25.751 --> 01:00:27.002
Want to fight?

01:00:28.545 --> 01:00:31.631
Kobeni! We're changing strategies!

01:00:32.883 --> 01:00:36.093
This one's a lot stronger than us!

01:00:36.094 --> 01:00:38.388
Time for a strategic retreat!

01:00:38.972 --> 01:00:40.432
Anyways, bye.

01:00:45.687 --> 01:00:48.272
My legs... My legs...

01:00:48.273 --> 01:00:50.108
My legs gave out...

01:00:51.318 --> 01:00:54.112
My legs... My legs...

01:00:59.117 --> 01:01:02.119
I'm sorry! I'm sorry!

01:01:02.120 --> 01:01:04.957
I'll quit my job. So please forgive me!

01:01:25.519 --> 01:01:26.520
There she is!

01:01:34.152 --> 01:01:37.905
Hey. Chainsaw's awake now.

01:01:37.906 --> 01:01:40.450
But the bomb girl's right behind us.

01:01:41.994 --> 01:01:44.036
Shit! Damn!

01:01:44.037 --> 01:01:47.039
The transmitter's broken on this car.

01:01:48.375 --> 01:01:50.127
What's wrong with this car?

01:01:51.253 --> 01:01:54.046
If it comes down to it,
I'm going to crash this car into her!

01:01:54.047 --> 01:01:56.800
I can't let her have Denji!

01:01:58.635 --> 01:02:00.386
What's going on?

01:02:00.387 --> 01:02:02.430
He's cutting the top of the car!

01:02:02.431 --> 01:02:03.640
Huh?

01:02:06.602 --> 01:02:07.894
Stop, Denji!

01:02:07.895 --> 01:02:09.897
You haven't had that much blood yet!

01:02:11.106 --> 01:02:14.233
It hurt so much,
I thought I was going to die.

01:02:14.234 --> 01:02:17.320
My brain's all mixed-up.

01:02:17.321 --> 01:02:19.948
But I spent some time
looking back on what's happened.

01:02:21.283 --> 01:02:24.202
And I just realized

01:02:24.203 --> 01:02:27.789
that every single girl I ever meet
always tries to kill me!

01:02:28.373 --> 01:02:32.126
Everyone always wants Chainsaw's heart!

01:02:32.127 --> 01:02:36.297
Doesn't anyone want Denji's heart? Huh?

01:02:36.298 --> 01:02:40.051
I really do like you, Denji. It's true.

01:02:40.052 --> 01:02:42.053
Huh? Really?

01:02:44.640 --> 01:02:47.976
Don't listen to the enemy!
You're so gullible!

01:02:50.270 --> 01:02:53.815
That was close.
I was about to get tricked.

01:02:54.399 --> 01:02:57.610
I don't know why you're trying to kill me.

01:02:57.611 --> 01:02:59.821
But I don't care!

01:03:00.531 --> 01:03:02.574
I've got Makima!

01:03:03.408 --> 01:03:04.825
Makima?

01:03:04.826 --> 01:03:09.455
Denji, I didn't know that witch
has got you in the palm of her hand.

01:03:09.456 --> 01:03:12.583
Then it would have been no use
even if we ran away together.

01:03:12.584 --> 01:03:14.252
Aw.

01:03:14.253 --> 01:03:17.589
I wish I never kissed you! Aw.

01:03:20.801 --> 01:03:22.134
If anyone else dies because of me,

01:03:22.135 --> 01:03:25.055
I'm going to have trouble getting
out of bed in the morning.

01:03:26.181 --> 01:03:28.850
I'm going to arrest you!

01:03:28.851 --> 01:03:30.852
Come here, Denji.

01:03:30.853 --> 01:03:34.605
I'm going to show you how we fight.

01:03:34.606 --> 01:03:37.317
Then show me!

01:04:00.174 --> 01:04:03.301
Denji. You're not applying
what you've learned.

01:04:03.302 --> 01:04:06.137
You can't just swing
your chainsaws around.

01:04:06.138 --> 01:04:08.931
You've got to understand
your own power better.

01:04:08.932 --> 01:04:10.058
Huh?

01:04:13.687 --> 01:04:14.730
Boom.

01:05:08.700 --> 01:05:09.993
Regeneration?

01:05:11.036 --> 01:05:12.620
So you were revving the engine

01:05:12.621 --> 01:05:14.915
before you got kicked.

01:05:49.241 --> 01:05:50.576
You Devil!

01:06:10.721 --> 01:06:12.973
<i>If I mess up even
a single move, I'm going to die.</i>

01:06:13.640 --> 01:06:17.102
<i>I can see the future,
but only a few seconds in advance.</i>

01:06:17.686 --> 01:06:20.063
<i>I don't know if my body
will be able to react in time.</i>

01:06:26.028 --> 01:06:27.654
<i>Perfect judgment.</i>

01:06:32.951 --> 01:06:34.161
<i>Perfect judgment.</i>

01:06:36.205 --> 01:06:37.998
<i>Perfect judgment.</i>

01:06:43.795 --> 01:06:45.214
<i>Perfect--</i>

01:06:52.679 --> 01:06:53.888
That was close!

01:06:53.889 --> 01:06:56.892
Sorry I'm late.

01:06:57.476 --> 01:07:00.061
This is the first time I've ever
wanted to be friends with a Devil!

01:07:00.062 --> 01:07:01.396
Here you go.

01:07:04.900 --> 01:07:07.068
Time-out!

01:07:07.069 --> 01:07:09.904
I'm anemic
and I'm almost naked over here.

01:07:09.905 --> 01:07:12.156
And you've got the two of you.
That's not fair.

01:07:12.157 --> 01:07:15.660
You're right. Should we give her a break?

01:07:15.661 --> 01:07:17.036
No.

01:07:17.037 --> 01:07:19.163
That's what he said. Sorry!

01:07:19.164 --> 01:07:20.374
The time-out is over.

01:07:26.588 --> 01:07:30.801
Lady Reze! Typhoon is here!

01:07:31.969 --> 01:07:33.887
That's not fair!

01:07:52.906 --> 01:07:53.991
It's okay.

01:07:54.825 --> 01:07:56.743
You're going to go to heaven.

01:08:01.999 --> 01:08:03.791
I'm going to take your blood.

01:08:03.792 --> 01:08:05.043
Sorry.

01:08:26.231 --> 01:08:29.066
A normal devil would have been dead.

01:08:29.067 --> 01:08:32.196
You're so impressive, Lord Chainsaw!
You're amazing!

01:08:33.113 --> 01:08:36.072
Your girlfriend has killed
too many people.

01:08:36.073 --> 01:08:39.453
If we let her run free,
then many more will die.

01:08:40.412 --> 01:08:43.080
Chainsaw. Make your choice.

01:08:43.081 --> 01:08:47.084
<i>Either let her kill you
and minimize the damage,</i>

01:08:47.085 --> 01:08:48.921
<i>or kill her instead.</i>

01:08:51.048 --> 01:08:54.301
Well, that's an easy decision.

01:08:55.426 --> 01:08:57.888
Reze is incredibly powerful, though.

01:08:59.973 --> 01:09:03.393
Shark, you know
about the Chainsaw Devil, right?

01:09:03.977 --> 01:09:07.481
If you don't want to die today,
then you should tell us what you know.

01:09:09.483 --> 01:09:12.652
Lord Chainsaw runs really fast!

01:09:12.653 --> 01:09:17.490
But when he goes places,
he doesn't just use his legs.

01:09:17.491 --> 01:09:20.201
He uses the chains on his chainsaws
to get around.

01:09:20.202 --> 01:09:22.077
He flings his chains through the air
and hooks them on buildings,

01:09:22.078 --> 01:09:24.121
and then he swings
from building to building!

01:09:24.122 --> 01:09:28.416
I see! Samurai Sword
draws his sword to get around.

01:09:28.417 --> 01:09:31.170
And Reze uses explosions.

01:09:31.171 --> 01:09:33.548
I need to apply my own powers too!

01:09:33.549 --> 01:09:36.843
Lord Chainsaw, you're a genius!
Lord Chainsaw, you're a genius!

01:09:36.844 --> 01:09:41.598
I should use chains to get around!
I see! I get it!

01:09:43.308 --> 01:09:46.102
That's right! That's right!

01:09:46.103 --> 01:09:47.978
I'm going to try it!

01:09:47.979 --> 01:09:50.899
- Beam! Turn into a shark!
- Okay!

01:09:53.359 --> 01:09:54.361
Huh?

01:09:55.445 --> 01:09:57.906
This is it!

01:09:59.199 --> 01:10:04.538
I'm going to use chains to control Beam,
and Beam is going to run like a horse!

01:10:06.164 --> 01:10:08.791
That's not it...
That's not it...

01:10:08.792 --> 01:10:11.377
Are you sure? I don't think that's it.

01:10:11.378 --> 01:10:14.338
I think you're supposed to shoot out
the chains from your arms

01:10:14.339 --> 01:10:16.007
and hook them onto buildings.

01:10:16.008 --> 01:10:19.760
Huh? This is the right way! Right, Beam?

01:10:19.761 --> 01:10:22.013
You're right! You're right! You're right!

01:10:22.014 --> 01:10:24.432
All right! Run, Beam!

01:10:24.433 --> 01:10:29.021
You're right! You're right!

01:10:36.653 --> 01:10:39.406
What are you doing?

01:10:40.282 --> 01:10:41.533
Denji!

01:10:42.159 --> 01:10:44.619
There you are, Chainsaw!

01:10:44.620 --> 01:10:48.248
Denji! I'm going to make you
regret coming back to life!

01:10:49.583 --> 01:10:53.794
Beam! Don't make me regret this!

01:10:53.795 --> 01:10:55.088
Okay!

01:10:57.299 --> 01:10:59.218
Damn! Those guys...

01:10:59.801 --> 01:11:01.219
It's a monster battle!

01:11:01.220 --> 01:11:04.097
We're just going to
have to sit it out and watch.

01:11:17.069 --> 01:11:20.071
You keep missing!

01:11:20.072 --> 01:11:21.864
You're like a cockroach.

01:11:21.865 --> 01:11:25.076
I'm tired of the explosions!

01:11:25.077 --> 01:11:27.371
Chainsaw!

01:11:38.090 --> 01:11:40.175
- Take that!
- Ouch!

01:11:42.219 --> 01:11:44.512
What a waste.

01:11:44.513 --> 01:11:47.181
I cut off a beautiful woman's leg.

01:11:47.182 --> 01:11:50.477
Lady Reze! Take my blood!

01:11:55.983 --> 01:11:57.900
Oh! Good!

01:11:57.901 --> 01:11:59.361
Wait, that's not good!

01:11:59.862 --> 01:12:02.906
This is crazy.

01:12:04.616 --> 01:12:05.617
Oh!

01:12:13.500 --> 01:12:15.043
Grab on to something!

01:12:15.794 --> 01:12:18.172
I can't! I can't!

01:12:27.389 --> 01:12:28.390
It's okay.

01:12:29.975 --> 01:12:32.894
It's okay! You can let go!

01:12:32.895 --> 01:12:36.899
If I'm going to die, I don't care!
It just means today was my day to die.

01:12:37.482 --> 01:12:38.901
I'll be fine.

01:12:39.610 --> 01:12:42.153
I've been ready to die for a long time.

01:13:09.389 --> 01:13:11.432
Why?

01:13:11.433 --> 01:13:13.392
Why did you touch my hand?

01:13:13.393 --> 01:13:16.230
- Do you want to die?
- Of course I don't want to die!

01:13:20.776 --> 01:13:23.695
How much did my lifespan
decrease just now?

01:13:27.282 --> 01:13:28.408
About two months.

01:13:35.707 --> 01:13:38.961
If you want to die,
then die somewhere far away from me.

01:13:40.003 --> 01:13:42.047
I can't take it anymore,
watching someone die

01:13:42.756 --> 01:13:44.383
right in front of me.

01:14:05.445 --> 01:14:07.906
Lord Chainsaw!
We're in trouble! Something's coming!

01:14:08.574 --> 01:14:10.492
Lord Chainsaw--

01:14:15.289 --> 01:14:17.124
Hmm? Huh?

01:14:39.897 --> 01:14:42.774
Lord Chainsaw!

01:15:46.255 --> 01:15:47.756
Whoa.

01:15:56.014 --> 01:15:57.933
You were hanging in there
for a pretty long time.

01:15:59.601 --> 01:16:00.811
But I think it's time now...

01:16:03.438 --> 01:16:04.940
to put an end to this.

01:16:16.243 --> 01:16:18.203
That was close!

01:16:19.371 --> 01:16:20.496
Beam!

01:16:20.497 --> 01:16:24.001
Lord Chainsaw!
I'll make sure you won't regret this!

01:16:34.553 --> 01:16:36.262
Hey! This is bad!

01:16:36.263 --> 01:16:38.723
He's going to turn the whole city
into mincemeat at this rate!

01:16:38.724 --> 01:16:42.560
Beam! We've got to get
that fat-ass to shut up first!

01:16:42.561 --> 01:16:43.729
Okay!

01:16:55.032 --> 01:16:57.034
I found you!

01:17:02.956 --> 01:17:06.543
Die! Chainsaw!

01:17:35.614 --> 01:17:36.782
Yeah!

01:17:37.491 --> 01:17:39.992
Beam! Send me flying!

01:17:39.993 --> 01:17:41.995
Yeah!

01:17:49.503 --> 01:17:52.296
This makes it easy for me!

01:17:52.297 --> 01:17:55.676
All I have to do
is swing my chainsaws around...

01:17:56.260 --> 01:17:59.388
like crazy!

01:18:03.600 --> 01:18:04.768
Whoa!

01:18:06.019 --> 01:18:08.312
Beam!

01:18:08.313 --> 01:18:11.149
Lord Chainsaw!

01:18:29.501 --> 01:18:31.919
Stay away!

01:18:35.632 --> 01:18:37.550
Come on!

01:19:12.669 --> 01:19:14.587
We did it! Beam!

01:19:14.588 --> 01:19:16.215
Where's Reze?

01:19:17.674 --> 01:19:19.343
Ah! Lord Chainsaw!

01:20:17.943 --> 01:20:19.278
Whoa!

01:21:06.033 --> 01:21:07.491
Ouch!

01:21:07.492 --> 01:21:09.118
You saved me, Beam!

01:21:12.247 --> 01:21:15.918
Denji. Don't you think
it's about time you gave up?

01:21:16.543 --> 01:21:17.878
Uh...

01:21:18.670 --> 01:21:19.671
No.

01:21:40.275 --> 01:21:44.196
You're being a huge pain in the ass.
Just hurry up and die already.

01:21:44.821 --> 01:21:50.077
Then you should have just
killed me when we first met!

01:21:52.204 --> 01:21:53.705
There's nowhere left to run.

01:21:54.456 --> 01:21:55.707
I wouldn't be so sure about that.

01:21:56.333 --> 01:21:59.919
You shouldn't have taught me how to swim.

01:21:59.920 --> 01:22:02.673
Huh... You're going to swim?

01:22:32.035 --> 01:22:33.453
Chains?

01:22:52.806 --> 01:22:56.935
Can you still explode when you're wet?

01:24:44.960 --> 01:24:46.420
I can't believe it.

01:24:47.462 --> 01:24:49.882
Why did you resurrect me?

01:24:52.259 --> 01:24:55.012
I have a great life.

01:24:55.679 --> 01:24:59.682
No matter how many times
I get beat up or die,

01:24:59.683 --> 01:25:03.353
as long as I get to eat good food
the next day, I can forgive.

01:25:04.730 --> 01:25:05.731
But...

01:25:07.191 --> 01:25:10.152
if I capture you and hand you over
to Public Safety,

01:25:10.736 --> 01:25:14.656
I'd feel like I had a fish bone
stuck in my throat.

01:25:18.827 --> 01:25:21.454
Even if I were living
a good life every day,

01:25:21.455 --> 01:25:24.833
it would feel bad, having something
poking the back of my throat.

01:25:30.255 --> 01:25:33.758
Do you think you would
still say that if I killed you right now?

01:25:35.636 --> 01:25:37.637
If someone's going to kill me,

01:25:37.638 --> 01:25:39.264
then I'd rather be killed
by a beautiful woman.

01:25:50.359 --> 01:25:51.568
Ah...

01:25:53.153 --> 01:25:58.242
Do you really still believe
that I like you for real?

01:25:59.368 --> 01:26:03.747
The look on my face when I met you,
and the way I blushed... It was all a lie.

01:26:04.665 --> 01:26:06.666
I just trained myself how to do it.

01:26:08.043 --> 01:26:10.212
I failed.

01:26:10.754 --> 01:26:13.507
I took too much time before I fought you.

01:26:15.133 --> 01:26:17.469
I'm going to run away now.

01:26:24.226 --> 01:26:25.811
Do you want to run away together?

01:26:27.271 --> 01:26:28.355
Huh?

01:26:29.147 --> 01:26:32.192
I can fight too.
You'll have a better chance at escaping.

01:26:34.236 --> 01:26:36.988
I killed lots of people.

01:26:36.989 --> 01:26:41.952
If you let me get away,
that would make you complicit in murder.

01:26:42.452 --> 01:26:43.996
Do you understand what that means?

01:26:45.205 --> 01:26:46.206
Uh...

01:26:46.790 --> 01:26:49.126
I know I shouldn't,
but I've got no choice.

01:26:49.626 --> 01:26:51.170
I still like you.

01:26:52.296 --> 01:26:54.130
You said it was all a lie.

01:26:54.131 --> 01:26:57.217
But you did teach me how to swim. Right?

01:27:39.426 --> 01:27:40.635
Hey!

01:27:40.636 --> 01:27:43.596
You should learn to be smarter.

01:27:43.597 --> 01:27:46.266
Reze! Hey, Reze!

01:27:51.855 --> 01:27:56.359
I'm going to be waiting
at the café at lunch!

01:27:56.360 --> 01:27:58.070
You'd better--

01:28:02.199 --> 01:28:05.118
Get up, Beam! My hand won't move!

01:28:06.286 --> 01:28:08.038
Rev up my engine!

01:28:52.583 --> 01:28:55.960
<i>There's a fairy tale
that mothers in the Soviet Union tell</i>

01:28:55.961 --> 01:28:57.045
<i>when scolding their children.</i>

01:28:58.172 --> 01:29:04.552
<i>The story says that there's a secret room
in the military's munitions storehouse.</i>

01:29:04.553 --> 01:29:06.555
And the secret room is filled
with orphans.

01:29:09.766 --> 01:29:12.268
The kids who live there
don't have any freedom.

01:29:12.269 --> 01:29:13.896
They're not allowed to go outside.

01:29:14.897 --> 01:29:16.439
They're treated like objects.

01:29:16.440 --> 01:29:19.443
And the military uses their bodies
for experiments until they die.

01:29:20.027 --> 01:29:22.571
It was supposed to be just a fairy tale.

01:29:23.071 --> 01:29:27.284
But one day, a newspaper reported that
that secret room really did exist.

01:29:28.160 --> 01:29:30.203
<i>An American journalist was the one
who uncovered the story.</i>

01:29:30.204 --> 01:29:32.164
<i>It was all over the news.</i>

01:29:32.664 --> 01:29:36.126
<i>They published photos
of the children who were there.</i>

01:29:36.627 --> 01:29:38.420
<i>But the story soon disappeared.</i>

01:29:39.004 --> 01:29:42.173
<i>The girl who lured Denji in
was one of the kids from that room.</i>

01:29:42.174 --> 01:29:43.299
TYPHOON DEVIL DAMAGE RELIEF FUND

01:29:43.300 --> 01:29:44.843
YOUR SUPPORT AND COOPERATION
ARE APPRECIATED

01:29:45.928 --> 01:29:49.598
A fighter created by the Soviet Union
to serve their country.

01:29:53.435 --> 01:29:56.939
<i>They're called guinea pigs.</i>

01:29:59.900 --> 01:30:04.321
<i>The Yamabiko train bound for
Sendai will soon depart from Platform 12.</i>

01:30:05.113 --> 01:30:07.114
<i>The next stop will be Ueno.</i>

01:30:07.115 --> 01:30:08.491
<i>The train will now depart.</i>

01:30:08.492 --> 01:30:10.743
<i>This is the Yamabiko train
bound for Sendai.</i>

01:30:10.744 --> 01:30:13.371
<i>The train will now depart.
Doors are closing.</i>

01:30:13.372 --> 01:30:15.457
<i>Please stand clear of the closing doors.</i>

01:31:28.155 --> 01:31:29.156
Me too.

01:31:31.867 --> 01:31:34.369
I like the country mouse too.

01:31:36.914 --> 01:31:40.292
One of my friends has a field
in the countryside.

01:31:41.168 --> 01:31:45.005
I go there to help out my friend
every year in the fall.

01:31:46.298 --> 01:31:51.011
The field has mice hiding in the soil
that damage the crops.

01:31:51.929 --> 01:31:56.058
We have to exterminate the mice
before the fields get covered in snow.

01:31:56.642 --> 01:32:02.105
So we dig up the fields and have the dogs
kill the mice hiding inside.

01:32:03.315 --> 01:32:04.525
I wonder why...

01:32:05.359 --> 01:32:06.944
whenever I watch...

01:32:08.362 --> 01:32:09.863
I feel so comforted.

01:32:15.327 --> 01:32:17.454
That's why I like the country mouse.

01:32:53.240 --> 01:32:54.324
<i>Why...</i>

01:32:55.367 --> 01:32:58.829
<i>I wonder why I didn't kill you
the first time we met.</i>

01:33:00.163 --> 01:33:03.208
<i>Denji, to be honest...</i>

01:33:04.960 --> 01:33:08.046
<i>I've never been to school either.</i>

01:33:21.185 --> 01:33:24.271
I told you to come with Hayakawa.

01:33:24.771 --> 01:33:28.358
You didn't want to make
Hayakawa kill a girl.

01:33:29.318 --> 01:33:30.527
You're so kind.

01:33:31.528 --> 01:33:33.906
It's because I'm an angel.

01:33:45.125 --> 01:33:46.126
Hey.

01:33:47.044 --> 01:33:48.712
Is the city a good place?

01:37:56.376 --> 01:37:59.421
Denji. I've got to close the café now.

01:38:01.006 --> 01:38:02.841
That girl was too cute.

01:38:03.509 --> 01:38:05.385
She was from a different world.

01:38:07.179 --> 01:38:10.974
I'm sure you'll meet a girl
who's perfect for you someday.

01:38:22.027 --> 01:38:23.695
RECOMMENDATIONS

01:38:37.543 --> 01:38:40.211
P-P-P-Power!

01:38:41.713 --> 01:38:47.134
I'm back! I tracked you down
by following your scent.

01:38:47.135 --> 01:38:49.721
What a tiny café!

01:38:56.895 --> 01:38:58.396
Hmm?

01:38:58.397 --> 01:39:01.107
Oh. What are you doing with those flowers?

01:39:01.108 --> 01:39:04.695
They would really suit me!
Give them to me!

01:39:19.209 --> 01:39:23.546
Hey! Don't eat them!
They're mine! You thief!

01:39:23.547 --> 01:39:25.590
You idiot!

01:39:25.591 --> 01:39:27.384
Spit them out right now!

01:39:27.885 --> 01:39:31.721
Spit them out! Spit them out!
